    <item>
      <title>南非在打击犯罪方面取得一定成效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/south-africa-showcases-some-success-in-fighting-crime-scourge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非警察局长表示，执法机构在打击南非犯罪祸害方面取得了重大进展，捣毁了一批犯罪团伙，缴获了数千件非法武器和大量毒品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/south-africa-showcases-some-success-in-fighting-crime-scourge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国在发生致命骚乱后禁止伊斯兰政党参与政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bangladesh-bans-islamist-party-from-politics-after-deadly-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国因涉嫌参与演变为暴力的学生抗议活动，正式禁止该国最大的伊斯兰政党参与一切政治活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bangladesh-bans-islamist-party-from-politics-after-deadly-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:34:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前《中国日报》编辑胡锡进因发表经济言论被社交媒体封禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ex-china-editor-hu-banned-on-social-media-after-post-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国官媒《环球时报》前总编辑胡锡进因发表针对世界第二大经济体的争议性言论而被禁止在社交媒体上发帖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ex-china-editor-hu-banned-on-social-media-after-post-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
